 Fixes
 =====
 
+- Fixed a regression introduced in 4.2.0 that caused queries with ``UNNEST``
+  with a single nested array as parameter to fail with a
+  ``ClassCastException``. For example::
+
+    SELECT x FROM unnest([[1, 2], [3]]) as t (x);
+
